_aChangeLog.text: Pakrat'd the map after three whole months -_-

_sText:
A medium sized bhop map for CS:S. This took about a month of on and off work. It has basic features like spikes, boosters, and of course bhop blocks. The reason it's called bhop_dood, is because I wanted to make a map with a similar name to bhop_dord, but be different entirely. I know "d00d" is an outdated term, but I like it. Also, in Hammer, the map looks like "dUUd," which is "d00d" with cut off zeros. Please rate the map after you play it!

Don't have CS:S? Get it for CS:GO here.

Re-Uploaded October 30, 2016.
